          <li>Social media management</li>
          <li>Web development and design</li>
          <li>Analytics and reporting</li>
          <li>Marketing consultation and strategy</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Client Responsibilities</h2>
        <p>As a client, you agree to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide accurate and complete information about your business</li>
          <li>Grant necessary access to accounts and platforms</li>
          <li>Respond to requests for information in a timely manner</li>
          <li>Review and approve deliverables within agreed timeframes</li>
          <li>Make payments according to the agreed schedule</li>
          <li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
          <li>Respect intellectual property rights</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Payment Terms</h2>
        <h3>Fees and Billing</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Service fees are billed monthly in advance</li>
          <li>Ad spend is billed separately and directly to advertising platforms</li>
          <li>Setup fees, if applicable, are due upon contract signing</li>
          <li>All fees are non-refundable unless otherwise specified</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Late Payments</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Payments are due within 30 days of invoice date</li>
          <li>Late payments may incur a 1.5% monthly service charge</li>
          <li>Services may be suspended for accounts over 60 days past due</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Contract Terms and Termination</h2>
        <h3>Contract Duration</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Services are provided on a month-to-month basis unless otherwise agreed</li>
          <li>Minimum engagement periods may apply to certain services</li>
          <li>Contract terms will be specified in individual service agreements</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Termination</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Either party may terminate with 30 days written notice</li>
          <li>Immediate termination may occur for breach of contract</li>
          <li>All outstanding fees are due upon termination</li>
          <li>Client data and access will be transferred upon request</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <h3>Client Content</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Clients retain ownership of their existing intellectual property</li>
          <li>Clients grant us license to use their content for service delivery</li>
          <li>We may use client work as case studies with permission</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Our Work Product</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom strategies and campaigns become client property upon payment</li>
          <li>We retain rights to our methodologies and processes</li>
          <li>Third-party tools and platforms remain property of their owners</li>
        </ul>

